page.title: 09A CHILDS DAY IN DETAIL
page.content: 7.30 Get up. 8.00 Dressed,having breakfast. 8.30 Standing on railway station. 8.45 Arrived at school. 9.00 Bell gone,in registration. 9.30 At first lesson,Maths. 10.00 Drawing a triangle diagram. 10.30 In Environmental Studies. 11.00 Bell gone,after break back to Environmental Studies. 11.30 Drawing a map of Chichester Harbour. 12.15 Finished work. 12.30 Walking around school. 1.00 Eating lunch. 1.30 Bell gone,having French lesson. 2.00 Going to Maths. 2.30 In a library lesson. 3.00 Reading book"Our Mums and Dads". 3.30 End of registration. 4.00 Standing on railway station.
